 1. SSH in — set root password or add your SSH key                              
 2. Firewall — ufw allow ssh && ufw enable                                      
 3. fail2ban — apt install fail2ban                                             
 4. Tailscale — install + tailscale up + remove old node from admin console     
 5. Tailscale Funnel — re-enable for the Gmail webhook endpoint                 
 6. Node.js — install v22 via nodesource                                        
 7. OpenClaw — npm install -g openclaw + openclaw init                          
 8. Clone workspace — git clone                                                 
 https://github.com/codeharmonizer/financier-ai-advisor.git into                
 ~/.openclaw/workspace                                                          
 9. OpenClaw config — restore openclaw.json (Gmail hooks, model, channels)      
 10. GitHub CLI — install gh + gh auth login                                    
 11. gog CLI — install + re-auth with claudealtenative@gmail.com                
 12. gcloud SDK — install + set project to financier-finsync                    
 13. Gmail Pub/Sub — update push subscription URL to new Funnel endpoint        
 14. Claude Code — install + configure                                          
 15. Start OpenClaw — openclaw gateway start    

That's it. ~15 steps, fresh server to fully operational.
